<title>THE GREAT VICTORY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngai un, Lalpa Jehovah,
 Sietlei dogal cheng Nuoisiehpa chu;
 Khawvel gitloh thawihna di'n Amah thi -
 San ngei chuh chawiin mun thiengtho A lut pih tai,
 Zie mun thiengtho a nga bang lengte chun;
 Kipahna la sa'n,
 Lalchutphah ma a ding, namtin laka mite;
 Pau tin laka mite leh thilhing lite chuh.

[V2]
 &quot;Zuomang Lalchutphah a chu leh,
 Belam No kawm achun;
 Lopina um hen&quot; tiin.

[V3]
 2. Aw, lei chung cheng cheng in le,
 Belam No gal zawhna la chuh sa'n;
 Kum khawsawta I do zawh ngei loh uh,
 Nuoi zinmang galhatpa tui bangin a tawm tai;
 Galzawhna lopi Belam No thisan,
 Zawhna lopi chuh;
 Chawian in la sai tiu, nuoi zinmang nuoisieh na'n,
 Lei mhiemte cheng cheng leh thilsiem cheng chengin.

[V4]
 3. Ngai un I van khawpi a van -
 Mi thiengtho nga bang lengsate chun;
 Belam No nunnem zawhna la hawih chuh -
 Sa'n kipakin sun leh zanin a chawl ngei puou;
 Van kingkang gihawih, van phaiphuleng gi-
 Hawih chitin chengin;
 Zawhna tumbak chawite hinna puon thieng silhte,
 Lalchutphah kimvel a chawihatna la hawih chuh.</lyrics>
</song>